From 3185e76da5d29a8c6dde75d17b17e73727264978 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Harish Rachakonda <rachakon@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Sat, 23 Aug 2025 22:18:10 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] QSDK:CP hostapd: ATF: addsupport for showatfstats

New vendor NL attributes and CLI commands to manage ATF
(Airtime Fairness) statistics reporting.
The following cli commands are added:

showatfstats
   - New NL attribute to get stats
   - CLI command: `showatfstats`

MLO:
hostapd_cli -i <ifname> [-l <link_id>] atf_offload showatfstats
SLO:
hostapd_cli -i <ifname> atf_offload showatfstats

Signed-off-by: Harish Rachakonda <rachakon@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
